data.description: Welcome to 2305 Kuykendall, a beautiful and upgraded home nestled in the heart of Bryan, Texas! This adorable 3 bedroom / 2 bath home is available in the Austin's Colony neighborhood on a cul-de-sac street! This spacious 1,877 sqft home has a great split floor plan with lots of natural lighting! Lovely living room with cozy double fireplace that mirrors the sitting room. Nice formal dining as well as breakfast nook. Completely updated kitchen: stainless steel appliances, new granite countertops, backsplash, tile flooring, and painted cabinets. Master suite is roomy!  Master bath has a walk in closet, separate shower, garden tub, double sinks, and new bathroom floor tile. Recent updates: HVAC, kitchen, flooring, paint, light fixtures. No carpet! This home also has extra decked out space in the attic for storage! Great backyard with patio! Call today to schedule your tour!
